    How to join our community ?

    To join us and help the needy animals, 
    1.  Fill the details in the below form and report us and wait for our response.
    2. Make sure to enter the correct details of the animal and the incident that happened to it. (Eg - Abandoned, Met an accident, etc)
    3. Upload a video or picture in youtube or other medium and provide the link in the form.
    4. Our team will contact you as soon as possible.

    For further details on us click on CLICK ME.
    Note - Donation is not mandatory.
